    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[About]]></title>
        <id>https://chris7462.github.io/music/2024/11/24/about</id>
        <link href="https://chris7462.github.io/music/2024/11/24/about"/>
        <updated>2024-11-24T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Playing the piano has been a childhood dream of mine — something I always wanted to do but never had the chance to pursue. In November 2024, I finally decided to make it happen.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Playing the piano has been a childhood dream of mine — something I always wanted to do but never had the chance to pursue. In November 2024, I finally decided to make it happen.</p>
<!-- -->
<p>I am entirely self-taught. Most of my learning comes from watching YouTube videos, studying how others play, and learning by ear. I'm still working on reading sheet music, so a lot of what I play is learned by observation and repetition rather than from notation.</p>
<p>This section of the site is where I share pieces I've been working on. They are not perfect, and that's okay — this is a journal of progress, not a recital.</p>]]></content>
